Give me my fucking money back!

01:46:02.731 --> 01:46:05.064
Fuck!

01:46:07.194 --> 01:46:08.184
Come on!

01:46:08.696 --> 01:46:11.530
- Give it back!
- What the fuck?

01:46:11.615 --> 01:46:13.277
No!

01:46:13.826 --> 01:46:15.192
Jesus Christ!

01:46:15.536 --> 01:46:18.279
You...

